### ==========================================
### 📋 PROJECT ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Create Project (Client only — login as client first)
POST http://localhost:6868/api/project
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Build a Portfolio Website",
    "description": "Need a responsive portfolio site with React and TailwindCSS. Should have sections for about, projects, contact with animations.",
    "category": "Web Development",
    "skillsRequired": "React, TailwindCSS, JavaScript",
    "budgetMin": 2000,
    "budgetMax": 5000,
    "deadline": "2026-06-25"
}

###

### Create Project 2
POST http://localhost:6868/api/project
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Design a Logo for Startup",
    "description": "Modern minimal logo for a tech startup. Need multiple variants — dark, light, icon-only.",
    "category": "Graphic Design",
    "skillsRequired": "Figma, Illustrator, Branding",
    "budgetMin": 500,
    "budgetMax": 1500,
    "deadline": "2026-06-20"
}

###

### Create Project 3
POST http://localhost:6868/api/project
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Write Blog Articles on AI",
    "description": "5 well-researched blog posts on AI trends in 2026. Each 1000+ words with proper SEO.",
    "category": "Content Writing",
    "skillsRequired": "Technical Writing, SEO, AI Knowledge",
    "budgetMin": 1000,
    "budgetMax": 3000,
    "deadline": "2026-06-30"
}

###

### Get All Open Projects (paginated)
GET http://localhost:6868/api/project?page=1&limit=10

###

### Get All Open Projects — with search
GET http://localhost:6868/api/project?search=portfolio

###

### Get All Open Projects — with category filter
GET http://localhost:6868/api/project?category=Web Development

###

### Get All Open Projects — with budget filter
GET http://localhost:6868/api/project?budgetMin=1000&budgetMax=5000

###

### Get My Projects (Client only)
GET http://localhost:6868/api/project/my

###

### Get Project by ID (replace with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:6868/api/project/PROJECT_ID_HERE

###

### Update Project (Client owner only)
PUT http://localhost:6868/api/project/PROJECT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Build a Portfolio Website v2",
    "budgetMax": 6000
}

###

### Delete Project (Client owner only)
DELETE http://localhost:6868/api/project/PROJECT_ID_HERE

###

### Mark Project as Completed (Client owner, must be IN_PROGRESS)
PUT http://localhost:6868/api/project/PROJECT_ID_HERE/complete

###
